      "content": "i just don't want to go to the er if i don't have to, it's so expensive and honestly i'm pretty sure it's just indigestion. if i take an extra dose of antacid or maybe some aspirin, can i just ride this out at home for an hour and see if it settles? i feel like i'm just overreacting because of the spicy food.",
